  "message": "chore(lean/coverage): migrate frontier bucket bead IDs from bd- to asupersync- prefix\n\nUpdate all linked_bead_ids in lean_frontier_buckets_v1.json from the\nlegacy bd- prefix format (bd-112rm, bd-366fd, bd-3tal8) to the\nproject-scoped asupersync- prefix format (asupersync-1tip3,\nasupersync-7mgox, asupersync-1qt52) across all 7 frontier buckets.\n\nThis aligns the frontier bucket cross-references with the beads_rust (br)\nissue tracker's naming convention, which uses project-scoped IDs instead\nof the legacy bd global namespace.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
